Making predictions

testing_predictions.2 <- data.frame(predict(model.2, newdata = celestial_testing)) %>%
  rename("output" = "predict.model.2..newdata...celestial_testing.")

submission.2 <- data.frame(c(celestial_testing, testing_predictions.2)) %>%
  select(id, output)
